ed="T" n="0848b24"/><persName key="A012858">釋契此</persName>者，不詳氏族<ptr target="#n2755"/>，或云<placeName key="PL000000012470">四明</placeName>人也。形裁<lb
ed="T" n="0848b25"/>腲脮<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1812"/>，蹙頞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1813"/>皤腹<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1814"/>，言語無恒，寢臥隨處。常以<lb
ed="T" n="0848b26"/>杖荷布囊入鄽肆<ptr type="glossary" target="#g640"/>，見物則乞，至于醯醬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g225"/>魚<lb
ed="T" n="0848b27"/>𦵔<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1815"/>，纔接入口，分少許入囊，號為<persName key="A012858">長汀子<lb
ed="T" n="0848b28"/>布袋師</persName>也<ptr target="#n2756"/>。曾於雪中臥，而身上無雪，人以<lb
ed="T" n="0848b29"/>此奇之。有偈云：「<persName key="A001428">彌勒</persName>真<persName key="A001428">彌勒</persName>，時人皆不識。<ptr target="#n638"/>」<pb ed="T" n="0848c" xml:id="T50.2061.0848c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0848c01"/>等句，人言<persName key="A001428">慈<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>垂迹也。又於大橋上立，或<lb
ed="T" n="0848c02"/>問：「<ref type="person" target="#A012858">和尚</ref>在此何為？」曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012858">我</ref>在此覓人。」<ptr target="#n639"/>常就人<lb
ed="T" n="0848c03"/>乞啜，其店則物售<ptr target="#n640"/>。袋囊中皆百一<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1061"/>──供身具也。<lb
ed="T" n="0848c04"/>示人吉凶，必現相表兆<ptr target="#n2758"/>。亢陽，即曳高齒木<lb
ed="T" n="0848c05"/>屐，市橋上竪膝而眠；水潦，則係<anchor xml:id="beg0848002"/>濕<anchor xml:id="end0848002"/>草屨<ptr target="#n2757"/>。人<lb
ed="T" n="0848c06"/>以此驗知。以<date notBefore-iso="+0901-05-18" key="j20502812051391" notAfter-iso="+0904-06-01"><name>天復</name>中</date>終于<placeName key="PL000000012481">奉川</placeName><ptr target="#n641"/>，鄉邑共埋<lb
ed="T" n="0848c07"/>之。後有他州見<ref type="person" target="#A012858">此公</ref>，亦荷布袋行<ptr target="#n2759"/>。<placeName key="PL000000000150">江</placeName><placeName key="PL000000008367">浙</placeName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0848c08"/>間多圖畫其像焉。</p>
